was, we had done many years of mobile optimization and we had built games as a

1212
00:58:50,255 --> 00:58:53,917
team together. We'd been through that original IP cycle four or five times.

1213
00:58:53,917 --> 00:58:58,080
And so we could sit down and throw out everything we'd ever learned about game

1214
00:58:58,080 --> 00:58:59,981
design and say, what works with this hardware?

1215
00:59:00,481 --> 00:59:02,802
And that was really the design process.

1216
00:59:02,802 --> 00:59:05,563
