1220
00:59:12,426 --> 00:59:15,987
So it was just give us the hardware, give us some time,

1221
00:59:15,987 --> 00:59:18,208
and see what comes out of it.

1222
00:59:18,208 --> 00:59:20,008
And that was their challenge.

1223
00:59:20,008 --> 00:59:22,529
